Package: interplot.medline
Type: Package
Title: A Wrapper for Interplot to Add Median Lines
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Tom Pepinsky
Maintainer: Tom Pepinsky <pepinsky@cornell.edu>
Description: This function is wrapper for the interplot function (Solt and Hu) that adds a median line to a standard marginal effects plot (Brambor, Clark, and Golder). It produces a minimally formatted plot with a histogram of the distribution of the moderating variable. 
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
  ggplot2,
  interplot
